Author: SHossain#0007
Content: You can't use PIRATE in Agama yet. Only CLI version

Author: SHossain#0007
Content:
`./komodod -ac_name=PIRATE -ac_supply=0 -ac_reward=25600000000 -ac_halving=77777 -ac_private=1 -addnode=136.243.102.225 -gen -genproclimit=x &`

`-genproclimit=x` replace x with the number of threads you want to use.
